’Ů@efc0fa58f88d118683b5d99bd1065a245355c476cef740c842b19065dbb0d7b2ŮăTitle: title: math arccos
Path: Examples
Content:
Get the arccosine of 1
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 1 | math arccos
0.0

```
Get the arccosine of -1 in degrees
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> -1 | math arccos --degrees
180.0

```
